item.title: Johns Hopkins University - Volodymyr Zelenskyy Makes Surprise Speech at 2023 Johns Hopkins Commencement
item.description: Video Transcript We could not be prouder that he’s joining us today from Ukraine where he is leading the struggle to keep his country free and Europe safe. Welcome, President Zelenskyy, to Johns Hopkins. (audience cheers and applauds) Thank you. Thank you very much. Thank you, Mrs. Applebaum, for such a generous and yet brief introduction. Mr. President Daniels, Mr. Chairman of the board of Trustees, Forster, dear students, faculty, parents, and guests
